race.description: Tab Calcutta 15 Jan Book Now Handicap
race.comment: Looks a wide open affair. ARTOPIA (5) has a handy record over this sprint trip with three wins and six plaings from 13 starts. Usually thereabouts and cannot be taken lightly. RUNAWAY TYCOON (2) is another first-up but looked to have come back in good order winning a Doomben trial and gets 3kg weight relief with the claim. In the mix. DARLING TAKE CARE (6) has placed over this course and distance and draws favourably in gate one. Sure to make her presence felt. CHAYSE'N'SCOTTY (11) resumes off a generous break. Has always shown glimpses of promise. Lone career win came at a previous first up outing.
